Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I CAN'T HEAR\NTHE FIREWORKS, PART 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Tonight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tonight I'm going to a fireworks display!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if Miss Fujiwara is a major pain,\Nfor this one night, I'll let it go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because she went as far as canceling\Na trip so she could go with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It really has been\Na boring summer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the first time, I'll go out with friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My first time\Ngoing out with the president.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I won't watch from the window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}because I finally get to go see\Nthe huge fireworks up close!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think that alone is enough for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to enjoy this whole summer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It really has been\Na boring summer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, your behavior\Nhas been unacceptable, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And with a large crowd,\Nit would be easy to lose sight of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If something happened to you\Nduring that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what would I say to your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure he wouldn't care.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}I'M SORRY.\NI WON'T BE ABLE TO GO TODAY.\NI'M REALLY SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}FROM: KAGUYA\NSUBJECT: I'M SORRY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm really sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I'd never known about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I hadn't known,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it would've been a normal summer,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I wouldn't have suffered like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... But it's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summer will be over soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}KAGUYA\NI'M A SECOND-YEAR HIGH SCHOOL STUDENT\NAT SHUCHIIN ACADEMY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}THANK YOU FOR CHECKING OUT MY PAGE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}KAGUYA / 5 DAYS AGO\NTHIS IS MY FIRST TWEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}KAGUYA / RIGHT NOW\NI WANT TO SEE THE FIREWORKS WITH EVERYONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}KAGUYA / RIGHT NOW\NI WANT TO SEE THE FIREWORKS WITH EVERYONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}KAGUYA / 5 DAYS AGO\NTHIS IS MY FIRST TWEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Kaguya, how long\Ndo you intend to lie there like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, by this point, you'd be sneaking\Nout of the house by hook or by crook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, it won't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't go shopping with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and my father has no interest\Nin me whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The president didn't even send me\Na single text this past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all has worked out for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I left the house right now,\Nit would be meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to see them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you'll see them once school starts\Nwhether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Misfortunes never come singly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When you're dejected,\Nyou really go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Certainly, you've been\Nthrough a rough summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But maybe not seeing President Shirogane\Nonce over vacation was the best choice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}if you think about it\Nfrom a long-term perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Time without seeing someone\Nmakes the heart fonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the president feels\Nthe same way you do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to see you so badly every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He counts on his fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how many days are left\Nof summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if he could somehow meet you\Nin a date with destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}his accumulated desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...would be set free all at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's right. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now you look like the Lady Kaguya I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But two of this house's butlers\Nare here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can escape from here\Nwithout any preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preparation, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WIRELESS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}J. SUZUKI OF KOENJI\NONE OF THE METRO AREA'S\NBIG FOUR RAMEN KINGS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to Hamamatsucho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Kaguya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a problem\Nwith that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She may be around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay here, Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The phone number you have called{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}is turned off or out of our service area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of the crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or because my phone is old?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, you want to go\Nsee the fireworks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's a lot of traffic tonight\Nwith all the cars out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I think you might not make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't make it in time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After what Hayasaka did for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why won't anything work out for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll go the rest of the way on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're supposed to meet up\Nat Takeshiba Wharf.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The main streets are really crowded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I run down a backstreet,\NI should be able to just make it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure I'll meet up with them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first younger student I've helped...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person who became my first friend...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first person I like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm in that circle of people!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}SHOPPING\NFIREWORKS FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}All summer,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the only thing I've been thinking about\Nis how happy I would be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if I got to gaze\Nat those beautiful fireworks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}together with my favorite people,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and how wonderful it would be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this summer,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't need love or romance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}So, at least let me be\Ntogether with them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...has concluded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you leave,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please pick up your trash,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}food and beverages.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this evening's fireworks display\Nhas concluded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you leave,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please pick up your trash,\Nfood and beverages.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, that's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no God.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if they enjoyed the fireworks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only got to see the fireworks\Nfrom between the buildings,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but they were so big.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For them, the fireworks\Nmust have looked beautiful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If everyone else got to enjoy them,\Nthat's enough for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll show them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Shinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna see them that badly,\NI'll show them to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the "Guess Shinomiya's Thoughts\Nand Search for Her" game?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to the usual,\Nit was 100 times easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaguya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President, I got us a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That young lady again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone hop in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}get on the expressway,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then take the Aqua-Line\Ntowards Umihotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are fireworks that were postponed\Nuntil tonight because of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Kisarazu fireworks display\Ngoes until 8:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can we get to Chiba\Nin the next 20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's worth the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna show Shinomiya\Nsome fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll step on it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is this cool driver?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,J. SUZUKI OF KOENJI\NONE OF THE METRO AREA'S\NBIG FOUR RAMEN KINGS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}God, let us be in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,President! I can't see anything outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Aqua-Line is an undersea tunnel!\NOf course you can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A sign for Umihotaru service parking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surfacing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us be in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let us be in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let us be in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their focus is on the fireworks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't take my eyes off of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}that face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound of my\Nheartbeat is so noisy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that I can't hear the fireworks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first day of the new school term.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone has come back\Nto their ordinary lives{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}with melancholy and hope in their hearts\Nafter a long, uneventful summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}KAGUYA DOESN'T WANT\NTO AVOID HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}One man looks back upon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}TRACING SHIROGANE'S EFFORTS\NSAVING A SPOT SIX HOURS\NBEFORE THE DISPLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}GETS THE NEWS THAT SHINOMIYA\NCAN'T GO, CALCULATES\NHOW SHE REALLY FEELS FROM HER TWEET
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}RIDES LIKE THE WIND\NTO SHINOMIYA'S FAMILY'S HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}USING BINOCULARS OUTSIDE THE HOUSE,\NREALIZES SHINOMIYA IS USING\NA "BODY DOUBLE" (HAYASAKA),\NGOES BACK THE WAY HE CAME AT MACH SPEED
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}MAKES CALCULATIONS IN HIS HEAD,\NFIGURES OUT THE ROUTE SHINOMIYA TOOK,\NDETERMINES HER LOCATION
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}USES THE EVENT INFO\NHE HAD INPUT EARLIER,\NRIDES LIKE THE WIND\NIN A TAXI TO KISARAZU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}PAYS THE CAB FARE TO THE TUNE\NOF 17,320 YEN (TAKEN FROM\NTHE POTENTIAL "SHINOMIYA\NSUMMER VACATION BUDGET")
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}USES THE EVENT INFO\NHE HAD INPUT EARLIER,\NRIDES LIKE THE WIND\NIN A TAXI TO KISARAZU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a memory he made at the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, I'll show them to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}And he regrets so much\Nthat he wishes he could die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mean the "Guess Shinomiya's Thoughts\Nand Search for Her" game?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ow! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dark past!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summer vacation was all but over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Shirogane hadn't seen\NShinomiya even once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}By the day of the fireworks,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shirogane was so tense\Nthat he couldn't hold it back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}There she is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That bursting tension caused him\Nto blurt out a series of cringeworthy lines!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Then, I'll show them to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You mean the "Guess Shinomiya's Thoughts\Nand Search for Her" game?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Compared to the usual,\Nit was 100 times easier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's worth the challenge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a dark past{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that will make him writhe in pain\Nwhen he recalls it for the next ten-odd years!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}If I saw Shinomiya now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what to say,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the words you said that night...\NHow can I put it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess you were like on an ego trip.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}President...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was painful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somebody, kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun this semester, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinomiya, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}STUDENT COUNCIL ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She won't even look at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She views me as someone\Nwho's too pathetic to look at directly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Shinomiya, about the other night—\N- Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's worse than I thought!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Look at all this dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She thinks of me as someone\Nwho's too pathetic to even be around!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wrong! Certainly,\NKaguya is avoiding Shirogane.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}But it's definitely not out of any ill will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}In fact, it's just the opposite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These actions are induced\Nby bashfulness and nervousness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Perhaps it might be called\N"like-avoidance."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Wh-Why am I avoiding him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I-It's like I'm self-conscious\Naround him or something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}HRRRMMM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Talk to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like you did\Nbefore summer vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to win Shinomiya's trust back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naturally, cheerfully...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I'll greet her naturally first!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}A straight line linked them\Nas they moved from opposite directions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A development that would certainly\Nmake them talk to each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Fujiwara,\Nwe need to clean the floor first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's hard to strike up a conversation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}They were both back in the saddle,\Nready to give it another go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}And yet the result was the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}No good! The closer I get to the president,\Nthe harder it is to look at him directly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}What kind of expression should I have\Nwhen I say something to Shinomiya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They continued to pass each other by,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just barely missing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}like two aircraft in a dogfight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But walking by each other twice\Nis unnatural.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it a coincidence?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. The president is being shy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, there's no need\Nfor me to be bashful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm totally calm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can do this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, I can go over to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can go over to her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An asterisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Fujiwara,\Nare you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mind on the cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are the rules of this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to talk to her\Nand clear up this misunderstanding!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see! It's not an asterisk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's a triangle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're mocking me, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Jeez, you don't get it at all,\Ndo you, Ishigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why are you suddenly\Nlooking down on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigami, am I really\Nthat amusing to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is over my head,\Nso I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ishigami was shot down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Ishigami. But four's a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three's a crowd, Miss Fujiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fujiwara was shot down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is going on here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I've been avoiding her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Shinomiya has been doing\Nthe same thing, too, repeatedly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she feels self-conscious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Calm down, Kaguya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Close your eyes! It'll be okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe she didn't think\NI was pathetic but actually cool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shirogane was back on his feet!{\i0}
